1. *Šef* je dao zadatak svim zaposlenima u firmi. (The boss gave a task to all the employees in the company.)

2. Ona je postala *šef* u svom odeljenju. (She became the boss in her department.)

3. On je postao *šef* svoje kompanije. (He became the head of his company.)

4. Njegov *šef* mu je dodelio novi projekat. (His boss assigned him a new project.)

5. Ona je postala *šef* nadređena njegovog tima. (She became the boss over his team.)

6. *Šefovi* bi trebalo da se čuvaju svojih zaposlenih. (Bosses should take care of their employees.)